    GetInputLangID(), GetInputLangName()
    Last submitted by teadrinker 20 Sep 2020 at https://www.autohotkey.com/boards/viewtopic.php?style=17&p=353708&sid=4498caf4025f947e56ee1f190c7f2227#p353708
